relevant_findings.general: No acute distress, alert and oriented to person, place, and time. No jaundice or scleral icterus.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs/rubs/gallops.
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear breath sounds but decreased throughout precordium.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Firmness to right upper quadrant with diffusely tender abdomen, no rebound tenderness but mild voluntary guarding.
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm, well-perfused, no cyanosis or edema.
